I"4<h1 id="basic-buttons">Basic Buttons</h1>

<p>A button can contain text. Although any tag can be used for a button, it will only be keyboard focusable if you use a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">button</code> tag or you add the property <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tabindex="0"</code>.</p>

